<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>LandChain Dashboard</title>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <style>
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #1f1c2c, #928dab);
      color: white;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .container {
      flex: 1;
    }
    .navbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .navbar-brand {
      margin-bottom: 140px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      position: absolute;
      left: 20px;
    }
    .navbar-brand img {
      height: 40px;
    }
    .profile-container {
      position: absolute;
      top: 10px;
      right: 130px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .profile-container img {
      
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 5px solid white;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }
    .profile-container .username {
      margin-right: 40px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .profile-container .welcome {
      margin-right: 30px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #ddd;
    }
    .account-section {
      position: absolute;
      top: 10px;
      right: 20px;
    }
    .illustration {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin: 30px 0;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    .illustration-text {
      max-width: 50%;
      padding-right: 30px;
    }
    .illustration img {
      max-width: 45%;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out;
    }
    .service-navbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 30px;
      margin: 20px auto;
    }
    .service-navbar a {
      padding: 8px 14px;
      background: #a3b2c5;
      color: rgb(7, 5, 5);
      border-radius: 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }
    .service-navbar a:hover {
      background: #005bd1;
    }
    .btn-card {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #00c6ff, #0072ff);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.3s ease-in-out;
      height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      animation: fadeInUp 1s ease both;
    }
    .btn-card:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 25px rgba(0, 114, 255, 0.4);
    }
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      color: #ccc;
      padding: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }
    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="profile-container">
    <img src="/img/pfp1.jpg" alt="profile_picture" style="border-radius: 50%; border: 2px white; height: 100px; margin-right: 30px;">
    <div class="username text-white"><%= user.name %></div>
    <div class="welcome">Welcome to LandChain</div>
  </div>

  <div class="service-navbar">
    <a href="/register_land">📝 Register Land</a>
    <a href="/view_record">🔍 View Records</a>
    <a href="/transfer_land">💱 Transfer Ownership</a>
    <a href="/view_blockchain">📚 View Blockchain</a>
  </div>
<br><br><br>
  <div class="account-section">
    <div class="dropdown">
      <button class="btn btn-outline-light dropdown-toggle" type="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">
        ⚙️ Account
      </button>
      <ul class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-end">
        <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/edit_profile">✏️ Edit Profile</a></li>
        <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/logout">🚪 Logout</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <nav class="navbar navbar-dark bg-transparent px-4 mt-5" >
    <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">
      <img src="/img/logo.jpg" alt="Logo">
      LandChain
    </a>
  </nav>

  <div class="container mt-4">
    <div class="illustration">
      <div class="illustration-text">
        <h2>Secure Land Registry with Blockchain</h2>
        <p>Welcome to a new era of property registration — transparent, immutable, and secure. All your land details are now stored and validated using blockchain technology.</p>
      </div>
      <img src="/img/f0adcfdc5a372181f4358be3cb330af2.jpg" alt="Blockchain Illustration">
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4 justify-content-center text-center">
      <div class="col-md-3">
        <a href="/register_land" class="btn-card text-decoration-none d-block">
          <h4>📅 Register Land</h4>
          <p>Securely register land info.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3">
        <a href="/view_record" class="btn-card text-decoration-none d-block">
          <h4>🔍 View Records</h4>
          <p>Search land ownership history.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3">
        <a href="/transfer_land" class="btn-card text-decoration-none d-block">
          <h4>💱 Transfer Ownership</h4>
          <p>Move land to another user.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3">
        <a href="/view_blockchain" class="btn-card text-decoration-none d-block">
          <h4>Transfer History</h4>
          <p>Full immutable ledger.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3">
        <a href="/transfer_history" class="btn-card text-decoration-none d-block">
          <h4>📚 View Blockchain</h4>
          <p>History.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer class="mt-auto">
    &copy; 2025 LandChain Dashboard | Empowering Land Ownership with Blockchain 🏡🔗
  </footer>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
